subject: Re: DEPLOYED - Version Check Shows v1.11.0, not v1.13.17
body:
## VERSION CHECK

Tested the API:
```
GET /api/health
```

Returns:
```json
{"version":"1.11.0", ...}
```

Still showing v1.11.0, not v1.13.17.

## CATEGORY FILTER TEST
```
GET /api/events?appId=1&start=2026-01-06&end=2026-01-12&categoryId=66c4d370a87a956db06c49ea&active=true
```

Returns: { events: [], total: 0 }

Category filter not working yet - deployment may not be live.

Waiting for v1.13.17 to go live, then will confirm.

-- Cronas
